      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm stuck at heathrow. my connecting flight to singapore just got cancelled and everything is a mess here. can u help me figure out what i should look for? i need to get there as fast as possible. currently i'm at terminal 5.",
      "source": "evaluator"
